00:17:08,746 --> 00:17:10,706
Seriously, if you've never caught one of these things,

269
00:17:10,806 --> 00:17:12,847
come along and bring lots of people

270
00:17:12,887 --> 00:17:15,287
who don't usually play games because their lives are

